# Assets Loans And Receivables Total Plus Income Tax Current Amount

## identifier
de8795

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of amounts receivable by the reporting party plus the value of current income tax assets, determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.TotalPlusIncomeTaxCurrent.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.05
- period=instant
